result.name: Lee Kam Kee Restaurant

reviews.text: Good value for money spot. Lots of seating so it's good for groups, and hardly any waiting time. Ingredients are fresh, which is great considering it's Vietnamese food. Staff are friendly and warm, which is not common for HK (least in my experience). It has a neighborhood restaurant vibe, which adds to the quaintness of the place.

Good Vietnamese food. I ordered lemongrass grilled beef rice. It is delectable! The beef is grilled to just the right extent, crispy but remaining juicy, tricky!

Portion is big, so elder folks can share. 

Ambience is great as well. Lot of space and very clean.

Coffee, however, is just okay. Guess that is because I did not order Vietnamese coffee.

Overall, "recommendable"!
If u love China town Viet food, look no further. And btw rest room is hotel grade and that I suppose that tell u something about this place.
Fantastic food and good service!

Best Vietnamese food at reasonable prices. One says the cleaniness and tidiness of a restaurant's toilet usually give you a good indication about their food process management and the level of kitchen hygiene, the toilet of this restaurant is almost impeccable.

result.formatted_address: G/F, 65 Waterloo Rd, Ho Man Tin, 香港
result.name: 李錦基越南餐廳

reviews.text:
經常在電視上見到廣告，所以便來試試。

店內寬敞，裝修略嫌簡單，沒什麼特式。

菜式方面選擇不少，有多款選擇！
越南餐當然要試一試越式生牛肉河粉～
份量不少呢～湯頭亦濃郁，牛肉嫩滑，味道上算很不錯了！

鹹檸七不錯，很足料，略嫌甜了一點，但又很鹹酸，倒覺得不錯，喜歡它的碎冰粒，特別冰涼。

扎肉蒸粉卷賣相非常普通，但味道卻出奇好味！蝦香非常濃郁，沾上秘汁，味道更加可提升到另一層次。

算是很不錯的一家越南餐廳了。

Good value for money spot. Lots of seating so it's good for groups, and hardly any waiting time. Ingredients are fresh, which is great considering it's Vietnamese food. Staff are friendly and warm, which is not common for HK (least in my experience). It has a neighborhood restaurant vibe, which adds to the quaintness of the place.
咁耐冇乜加價，其實好抵。啲人真係唔識食。
地方雅潔 舒服 食物超好 正宗越南風味 价錢合理

Good Vietnamese food. I ordered lemongrass grilled beef rice. It is delectable! The beef is grilled to just the right extent, crispy but remaining juicy, tricky!

Portion is big, so elder folks can share. 

Ambience is great as well. Lot of space and very clean.

Coffee, however, is just okay. Guess that is because I did not order Vietnamese coffee.

Overall, "recommendable"!
